OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Giorgio
OL,4,CArmani dies aged 91
OL,6,FItalian fashion designer Giorgio
OL,7,FArmani has died at home aged 91, his
OL,8,Fcompany confirmed on Thursday.
OL,10,FArmani, one of the most recognisable
OL,11,Fnames and faces in the global fashion
OL,12,Findustry, missed Milan Fashion Week in
OL,13,FJune 2025 for the first time during
OL,14,Fthe previews of Spring-Summer 2026
OL,15,Fmenswear to recover from an
OL,16,Fundisclosed condition.
OL,18,FHe was planning a major event to
OL,19,Fcelebrate 50 years of his signature
OL,20,FGiorgio Armani fashion house during
OL,21,FMilan Fashion Week this month.
