OL,6,FStarting with an unlined jacket,
OL,7,Fsimple trousers and an urban palette,
OL,8,FArmani put Italian ready-to-wear style
OL,9,Fon the global fashion map in the late
OL,10,F1970s, creating the relaxed silhouette
OL,11,Fthat defined his brand for the next
OL,12,Fhalf-century.
OL,14,FFrom boardrooms to Hollywood, Armani
OL,15,Fdressed the rich and famous in classic
OL,16,Ftailored designs made from soft
OL,17,Ffabrics and muted tones.
OL,19,FHis sharp black-tie suits and
OL,20,Fglittering gowns often stole the
OL,21,Fspotlight on red carpet nights.
